            <abstract>
                <p>Central theme of this prayer is the announcement to <persName ref="PRS3725Elizabet">Elizabeth</persName> of the 
                    difficulties she will experience during the birth of <persName ref="PRS5741Johnthe"/>, and the intervention of 
                    <persName ref="PRS8417Salome"/>, who is referred to as <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘይእቲ፡ ማኅረሲት፡ ወጠባብ፡ ጥቀ፡</foreign>. 
                    Salome acts as a female magician pronouncing magic names (ʾasmāt) over the woman in labour, being an allusion to the
                    <ref cRef="betmas:LIT2713Luke.chapter1">Gospel of Luke, chapter 1</ref>.</p>
            </abstract>
